  <description type="morphology">Trees  to 44m; trunk to 2.3m diam.; crown broadly conic.  Twigs  slender, glabrous or pubescent.  Leaves  (20--)25--45 × 1--1.5mm, bluish green, apex mucronulate.  Pollen cones  pale yellow.  Seed cones  9--20 × 4--7cm.  Seeds  9--12mm. 2 n =24.</description>
